data.description: This custom-built residence nestled in a prestigious gated community offers luxury living on over an acre! With attention to detail at every turn, this home is designed to exceed your expectations. The home offers a formal dining room and formal living room boasting a cozy gas fireplace and built-ins, creating a warm atmosphere. The home is equipped with Travertine throughout the main living areas and carpet in the bedrooms. The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen, complete with custom cabinets, double ovens, solid surface countertops, a center island, breakfast bar, pantry, and breakfast area that are adjacent to your family room! Additionally, there are 4 bedrooms and a study with built-ins. Escape to the luxurious primary suite, where the primary bath boasts a soaking tub, separate tiled shower, and dual vanities. Enjoy your outdoor amenities that include an in-ground, saltwater pool, and a pool house that features an outdoor shower, toilet, and sink providing the perfect space to unwind after a refreshing swim. Take in the serene ambiance of the screened back porch. This residence offers a perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and privacy.
